    <subfield code="a">• Preliminary assessment for two options of remote maintenance is carried out to establish a feasible maintenance scheme on the DEMO design. • Analysis on the plasma vertical stability indicates that the vertical maintenance scheme is the most effective on plasma vertical stability. • Design and preliminary assessment of in-vessel transferring mechanism and pipe connection were investigated.</subfield>
